                     <interp inst="t18160710-94-person682" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I picked up the hat the other boy escaped.</p>

               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>

               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was going for an errand for my mother, and I saw a parcel of boys running, and I ran.</p>

               <p>
